    <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-1">Skills That Transfer</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Anagramming ability, vocabulary knowledge, rack management, hook awareness, and general crossword-building intuition all transfer perfectly between both games.</p>
